snippet.title: My Haunted Doll Official Steam Trailer - A 2D Survival Horror Game
snippet.description:
Check this game out on Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/1181470/

My Haunted Doll is a 2D Survival Horror game based on the story of the cursed doll of the 1800s which is said to be possessed by the spirits of a little girl and the Devil. 

Tags: survival horror game, indie game, steam game, halloween special,
